Sheet 1: Unit Test Information
1.0a






















Nexteer EPS Unit Test Tool






Rev:2.7d












Name of Tester: Rasika Deshpande
Source files to be added to the .pjt file Must include path from 'Source Code Directory' setting on the Unit Test Tool Options dialog Include Files:

Code File(s) Under Test: PwmCdd.c



Code File(s) Version: 2



Module Design Document: PWM_CDD_MDD.docx



Module Design Document Version: 7



Data Dictionary Version: 6



Unit Test Plan Version: 5



Optimization Level: Level 2



Compiler (CodeGen) Version: Tms470_4.9.5



Model Type: Excel Macro



Model Version: Nexteer EPS Unit Test Tool 2.7d/ EPS Libraray 1.30



Total FLASH Used (Bytes): 9980



Total RAM Used (Bytes): 72



Total CALS Used (Bytes): 4



Special Test Requirements:




Test Date: 2/8/2014



Comments: NOTE1: Inline function defined in globalmarco.h is not unit tested.

NOTE2: In PwmCdd_Per1 function, offset logic is added for Phase_Rev_T_u0p16 and PhaseIndex_Rev_T_u0p16 variables while unit testing to avoid failures in the VBA code.

NOTE3: In ModIndxPhase_u0p16 function, coverage is not 100% due to the usage of FPM_InitFixedPoint_m macro for d_240Deg_Rev_u0p16 and d_120Deg_Rev_u0p16 constants.

NOTE4: In CDD_ApplyPWMMtrElecMechPol function, coverage is not 100% due to the usage of FPM_InitFixedPoint_m macro for d_PhaseAOffsetNrm_Rev_u0p16 , d_PhaseBOffsetNrm_Rev_u0p16, d_PhaseCOffsetNrm_Rev_u0p16,d_PhaseAOffsetInv_Rev_u0p16,d_PhaseBOffsetInv_Rev_u0p16 and d_PhaseCOffsetInv_Rev_u0p16 constants."

NOTE5: In "PwmCdd_Per1" function, "CDD_Read_CorrectedMtrPos_Rev_u0p16" is #define to "CDD_MtrPosElec_Rev_G_u0p16[CDD_CDDDataAccessBfr_Cnt_G_u16]" in "PwmCdd_Cfg.h" header file. Hence in VBA "CDD_MtrPosElec_Rev_G_u0p16[CDD_CDDDataAccessBfr_Cnt_G_u16]"is taken as input.

NOTE6: In PwmCdd_Per1 Function following array variables are going out of range :
i)CDD_PWMDutyCycleASum_Cnt_G_u32[2]
ii)CDD_PWMDutyCycleBSum_Cnt_G_u32[2]
iii)CDD_PWMDutyCycleCSum_Cnt_G_u32[2]
iv)CDD_PWMPeriodSum_Cnt_G_u32[2]

NOTE7:In "PwmPeriodDither_u16" function,offset logic is added to avoid failures in the VBA code while unit testing

NOTE8:The map file "CBD_Sandbox_dbg.map" is embedded for reference.
